person" ref="#pmb2173" subtype="implied">Frau</rs>!</p><closer>Mit den herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten Grüßen<lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>Max Mell.</signed></closer></div></body><back><listPerson><tei:person xml:id="pmb12225">
